projName: README Markdown Generator for GitHub Repositories
projDesc: Creates a Markdown file to include in your GitHub Repository.
projSteps: 1. install node.js 2. create node packages manager ```npm init -y``` 3. include inquirer v8.2.4 ```npm i inquirer@8.2.4``` 4. run ```node index.js```
projTest: No testing procedures at this time.
